{"tid":814321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台媒踢爆90%黑糖鮮奶店用假黑糖 焦糖色素或致癌及神經中毒","createTime":"2018-09-11T07:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T08:17:11.000Z","uid":5134,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cb13a87a22807b6c13e4a1074df5479f67421f27","tid":814321,"uid":5134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"黑糖鮮奶味道好加上有養生功效，難怪造就黑糖飲料於短時間爆紅，每間台飲品門前都大排長龍。繼老虎堂被踢爆用糖漿及焦糖色素，最近有台媒再爆市面上號稱手工製作的古法黑糖，超過9成店家用粗糖再製的還原黑糖，不但沒有養生之效，更可能致癌！<br />\n<img src=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/original/20180911124529_8_bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Foriginal%2F20180911124529_8_bb.jpg&h=af385d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲多杯~~<br />\n<img src=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/original/20180911123555_3_b2.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Foriginal%2F20180911123555_3_b2.PNG&h=c0734f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/24851/%E5%8F%B0%E5%AA%92%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%8690-%E9%BB%91%E7%B3%96%E9%AE%AE%E5%A5%B6%E5%BA%97%E7%94%A8%E5%81%87%E9%BB%91%E7%B3%96-%E7%84%A6%E7%B3%96%E8%89%B2%E7%B4%A0%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E7%99%8C%E5%8F%8A%E7%A5%9E%E7%B6%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F24851%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25AA%2592%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E7%2588%258690-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E7%25B3%2596%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2581%2587%25E9%25BB%2591%25E7%25B3%2596-%25E7%2584%25A6%25E7%25B3%2596%25E8%2589%25B2%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%2587%25B4%25E7%2599%258C%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25B6%2593%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592%2F1&d=tYIKVQDHuTuwEEk%2FJ6p%2FTMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=455965d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news